sp_scores.title: Defeat the Blue Dragon without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: The Blue Dragon has an arsenal of water attacks that hit the whole party, kupo! Brace for the deluge with Magic Break and Shell, then exploit its weakness to lightning with abilities like Thundaga and Thundara Strike!
tip_battle.title: Blue Dragon

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Magitek Armor without being KO'd.
Exploit the Magitek Armor's weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: Short-circuit Magitek Armor with lightning attacks before it pummels you with Magitek Laser and Metal Kick, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Magitek Armor

sp_scores.title: Defeat Ymir without triggering its counterattack.

tip_battle.message: Never, ever, EVER attack Ymir's shell, kupo, unless you want it to counterattack with Megavolt! Stay away from attacks and abilities that hit all targets so you don't hit the shell by accident!
tip_battle.title: Ymir

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Phantom Train without being KO'd.
Exploit the Phantom Train's weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: The Phantom Train has a lot of abilities that hit the whole party, so keep an eye on everyone's health! And it may look like a machine, but it's actually undead, so use fire and healing abilities, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Phantom Train

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Tentacles without being KO'd.
Exploit Tentacle (Bottom-Left)'s weakness to fire attacks.

tip_battle.message: Each of the four Tentacles has a different vulnerability, kupo. Use the right element on the right tentacle, or you'll end up healing them!
tip_battle.title: Tentacles

sp_scores.title: Exploit Orthros's weakness to fire attacks.

tip_battle.message: Orthros will use his Ink ability to Blind you, kupo. Not good! Try to make room in your abilities for Blindna so you can get rid of that debuff!
tip_battle.title: Orthros

tip_battle.message: If you don't bring down the 2 Ipoohs that appear with Vargas, you won't be able to hurt him, kupo! Exploit the Ipoohs' weakness to fire to take them down first!
tip_battle.title: Vargas

sp_scores.title: Defeat Ultima Weapon without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Ultima Weapon packs powerful magic attacks, kupo, and it doesn't have any special vulnerabilities. Weaken it with abilities like Armor Break, Power Break, and Magic Break!
tip_battle.title: Ultima Weapon
